Class Scenegraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • sgraph.Scenegraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IScenegraph

    public class Scenegraph
extends java.lang.Object
implements IScenegraph
    A specific implementation of this scene graph. This implementation is still independent of the rendering technology (i.e. OpenGL)
    Author:
    Amit Shesh
